0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ModelScope：<a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-5.1</a></span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">官方API接入</span></span></p>\n      <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n       <li>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">BigModel开放平台：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/text/glm-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/models/text/glm-5.1</a></span></span></p>\n       </li>\n       <li>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Z.ai：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://docs.z.ai/guides/llm/glm-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.z.ai/guides/llm/glm-5.1</a></span></span></p>\n       </li>\n      </ul>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">Blog</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://z.ai/blog/glm-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://z.ai/blog/glm-5.1</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">代码能力是模型智能水平进一步提升的关键。下图是</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">GLM-5.1分别在&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SWE-Bench Pro、Terminal-Bench 2.0、NL2Repo基准中的表现，综合结果上，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">取得了全球模型第三、国产模型第一、开源模型第一的成绩。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mnow4sai19l9\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5907407407407408\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;width: 676.989px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-backw=\"576\" data-backh=\"340\" data-imgfileid=\"100010039\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d401f977&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlRIrvTGkm9siboEzBBWAfiajGiaH71ricz8klRcM6z7GyBibVMJiaQcM5pyZib9bKicE683w6nNo63mXQg2XWEeWpczXjd1IjqRWPSTcQj1hc08RwqU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在最接近真实软件开发的SWE-bench Pro基准测试中，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">GLM-5.1刷新全球最佳成绩，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">超过GPT-5.4、Claude Opus 4.6。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mnow57xq1jwf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5416666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;aspect-ratio: calc(1.84615) / 1;width: 677px !important;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"576\" data-backh=\"312\" data-imgfileid=\"100010038\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a144a8b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlRIrvTGkm9u9wibGCb45Gfdpjl1ONSFvaWgSI3eAG80UKw3hIe6xGdhlVXYJiafic2MEiaQbSUpPwLG150rrbKJN4GbQMKJzA30qwKlicqI4oQ94%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <h2><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">案例展示：模型上班的8小时</span></span></h2>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">抛开Benchmark，本次 GLM-5.1 的官方展示重点，转向了：模型在长程任务中能否持续工作、持续优化，并完成完整的“执行、分析、修正”闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在同等评估口径下，GLM-5.1 展现出较强的长时间自主工作能力。以下是官方提供的三个案例：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Case 1：8小时从零构建 Linux 桌面</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在该任务中，模型被要求从零开始完成一个 Linux 桌面系统构建。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">任务结果：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">持续执行 8 小时</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">完成 1200+ 步操作</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">约 20 分钟后产生首个有效结果</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最终产出包含桌面、窗口管理器、状态栏、应用程序、VPN 管理器、中文字体支持、游戏库等完整组件</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生成配套文件约 4.8MB</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <div></div>\n  <p></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">Case 2：655 次迭代优化向量数据库</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">在向量数据库优化任务中，GLM-5.1 通过持续迭代完成性能提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">任务结果：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">655 轮迭代</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">持续进行 Benchmark 运行、瓶颈定位与方案调整</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">优化路径覆盖全库扫描、IVF 分桶召回、半精度压缩、量化粗排、两级路由、提前剪枝等</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">查询吞吐从 3108 QPS 提升至 21472 QPS</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">相比初始正式版本提升 6.9 倍</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">Case 3：1000 轮工具调用优化真实机器学习负载</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">在 KernelBench Level 3 基准上，GLM-5.1 针对 50 个真实机器学习计算负载进行持续优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">任务结果：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">超过 24 小时不间断迭代</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">完成多轮编译、测试、分析、重写循环</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">支持 Triton Kernel、CUDA Kernel、cuBLASLt epilogue 融合、shared memory tiling、CUDA Graph 等优化方式</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">几何平均加速比达到 3.6 倍</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">对比 torch.compile max-autotune 模式的 1.49 倍，提升更明显</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:medium;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mnow8cth1ysp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;aspect-ratio: calc(2) / 1;width: 677px !important;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"576\" data-backh=\"288\" data-imgfileid=\"100010037\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4aba620&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlRIrvTGkm9uWN4q8OhickUib3864icsax35Xks2MV3ibgFXsUpIXbibicljDV921pYQ5suH6r1SXjDDJ7oluPibhJ7GiaOZic1D9KnyBQLrCgO7YNibxQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n  <h2><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以上三个场景共同指向同一个核心变量：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">真正决定模型能力的，并不是运行时长本身，而是额外的运行时间是否仍然有效</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。GLM-5.1 相较 GLM-5 将这一有效工作窗口显著地向后延伸，而 KernelBench 上仍然存在的差距也说明，长程优化依旧是一片有待开拓的前沿。</span></span></h2>\n  <h2><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">前路仍有诸多挑战：如何在增量调优不再奏效时更早跳出局部最优，如何在跨越数千次工具调用的执行轨迹中保持连贯性，以及，也是最重要的，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">如何在没有数值指标的任务上建立可靠的自我评估机制</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。GLM-5.1 是智谱团队在这个方向上迈出的第一步，后续仍会持续推进。</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;heading&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:2},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">模型实战指引</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以下开源框架支持 GLM-5.1 的本地部署：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">SGLang (v0.5.10+)：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://cookbook.sglang.io/autoregressive/GLM/GLM-5.1\" target=\"_blank\">https://cookbook.sglang.io/autoregressive/GLM/GLM-5.1</a></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-weight:bold;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">vLLM (v0.19.0+)：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/vllm-project/recipes/blob/main/GLM/GLM5.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/vllm-project/recipes/blob/main/GLM/GLM5.md</a></span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-weight:bold;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">xLLM (v0.8.0+)：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-5/blob/main/example/ascend.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-5/blob/main/example/ascend.md</a></span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-weight:bold;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Transformers (v0.5.3+) ：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/huggingface/transformers/blob/main/docs/source/en/model_doc/glm_moe_dsa.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/huggingface/transformers/blob/main/docs/source/en/model_doc/glm_moe_dsa.md</a></span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">KTransformers (v0.5.3+) ：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/kvcache-ai/ktransformers/blob/main/doc/en/kt-kernel/GLM-5.1-Tutorial.md\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/kvcache-ai/ktransformers/blob/main/doc/en/kt-kernel/GLM-5.1-Tutorial.md</a></span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">点击</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">阅读原文，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即可跳转模型合集接~</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱发布旗舰开源模型 GLM-5.1，主打 8 小时长程任务自主执行能力，在 SWE-bench Pro 等多项代码基准测试中取得领先成绩。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱发布旗舰开源模型 GLM-5.1，主打 8 小时长程任务自主执行能力，在 SWE-bench Pro 等多项代码基准测试中取得领先成绩。",
  "summary": "智谱 AI 正式发布并开源其旗舰模型 GLM-5.1。该模型的核心突破在于「长程任务（Long-Horizon Task）」处理能力，能够连续自主工作超过 8 小时，实现从自主规划、执行到自我迭代的全流程闭环，无需人工干预。在 SWE-bench Pro 基准测试中，其表现超过了 GPT-5.4 和 Claude Opus 4.6。文章通过构建 Linux 桌面、优化向量数据库性能（提升 6.9 倍）以及优化机器学习负载（加速 3.6 倍）三个实战案例，展示了模型在长时间跨度下的有效工作能力。目前该模型已在 GitHub 和 ModelScope 开源，并支持 vLLM、SGLang 等主流推理框架。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GLM-5.1 实现了从「助手」向「工程师」的角色转变。",
      "explanation": "模型不再局限于短时间的对话或单次任务，而是具备了长达 8 小时的自主工作窗口，能够处理涉及上千步操作的复杂工程任务。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在多项权威代码基准测试中刷新纪录。",
      "explanation": "在 SWE-bench Pro、Terminal-Bench 2.0 等测试中取得全球前三、开源第一的成绩，证明了其在真实软件开发环境下的极强竞争力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过持续迭代实现显著的性能优化效果。",
      "explanation": "案例显示模型能通过数百轮迭代，自主定位瓶颈并应用量化、剪枝、Kernel 融合等高级优化手段，使系统吞吐量提升数倍。"
    },
    {
      "point": "长程任务仍面临自我评估与跳出局部最优的挑战。",
      "explanation": "尽管取得了突破，但在跨越数千次工具调用的连贯性保持，以及缺乏数值指标时的自我评估机制方面，仍是未来探索的前沿。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "一次下发，模型即可自主规划、执行、自我迭代，全程无需人工接管，最终交付完整的工程级成果。",
    "真正决定模型能力的，并不是运行时长本身，而是额外的运行时间是否仍然有效。",
    "GLM-5.1 刷新全球最佳成绩，超过 GPT-5.4、Claude Opus 4.6。",
    "如何在增量调优不再奏效时更早跳出局部最优，如何在跨越数千次工具调用的执行轨迹中保持连贯性。"
  ],
